→ development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/commands/configure[configure] → development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/commands/configure#rman-configure-device-type[device type] → development/databases/Oracle/tools/RMAN/SBT[sbt]  backup type to compressed backupset;
code }

}

